name: The Texan
overview: The Texan was a Western television series starring popular B movie actor Rory Calhoun, which aired on the CBS television network from 1958 to 1960.

episodes.name: The Man with the Solid Gold Star
The Troubled Town
episodes.overview: There is a card shark that didn't appreciate having his cheating be revealed, even if it was subtle. He is gunned down in the street. His brothers seek revenge, one brother is a little more cautious than the other. He wants to make sure they get the person who did the shooting or that the sheriff locates the person.
